Indeed. You would have to poll the endpoints you want to monitor periodically and obviously the hit counter will reset when the object is expired/purged.<p>Something like<p><pre><code>  sub vcl_deliver {
    if (client.ip == &quot;127.0.0.1&quot;) { # or header/method/whatever
      set resp.http.X-Cache-Hits = resp.hits;
    }
  }</code></pre>
